#################################### Comorbidities ########################################################################################

Sys.setenv(LANG = "en")
library(readxl)
library(tidyverse)
library(dplyr)

#df <- readRDS("df_allyears_dx_dx_pr.rds")

dict_comorb <- read_excel("CMR-Reference-File-v2022-1.xlsx", sheet = 3, skip = 1)
AIDS <- filter(dict_comorb, AIDS ==1)
AIDS <- dput(unlist(AIDS[,1]))
ALCOHOL <- filter(dict_comorb, ALCOHOL ==1)

#################################################################################################
############################# Charlson comorbidity index ########################################
#################################################################################################

Sys.setenv(LANG = "en")
library(readxl)
#library(tidyverse)
library(dplyr)
library(haven)

df <- readRDS("df_allyears_updated_variables.rds")

df$index <- 1:nrow(df)

df_cci <- select(df, c("index", "I10_DX1", "I10_DX2", "I10_DX3", "I10_DX4", "I10_DX5", "I10_DX6", "I10_DX7", "I10_DX8", "I10_DX9", "I10_DX10", "I10_DX11", "I10_DX12", "I10_DX13", "I10_DX14", "I10_DX15", "I10_DX16", "I10_DX17", "I10_DX18", "I10_DX19", "I10_DX20", "I10_DX21", "I10_DX22", "I10_DX23", "I10_DX24", "I10_DX25", "I10_DX26", "I10_DX27", "I10_DX28", "I10_DX29", "I10_DX30", "I10_DX31", "I10_DX32", "I10_DX33", "I10_DX34", "I10_DX35", "I10_DX36", "I10_DX37", "I10_DX38", "I10_DX39", "I10_DX40"))

df_cci <- df_cci %>% 
  pivot_longer(
    cols = starts_with("I10_DX"), 
    names_to = "I10_DX", 
    names_prefix = "I10_DX",
    values_drop_na = TRUE,
  )

charlson_comorbidities <- comorbidity(df_cci, id = "index", code = "value", map = "charlson_icd10_quan", assign0 = TRUE, labelled = TRUE, tidy.codes = TRUE)

charlson_score <- score(charlson_comorbidities, weights = "quan", assign0 = TRUE)

df <- cbind(df, data.frame(charlson_score))

elixhauser_comorbidities <- comorbidity(df_cci, id = "index", code = "value", map = "elixhauser_icd10_quan", assign0 = TRUE, labelled = TRUE, tidy.codes = TRUE)
elixhauser_score <- score(elixhauser_comorbidities, weights = "swiss", assign0 = TRUE)

df <- cbind(df, data.frame(elixhauser_score))

saveRDS(df, file = "df_allyears_updated_variables_score.rds")

Sys.setenv(LANG = "en")
library(readxl)
library(tidyverse)
library(dplyr)

df <- readRDS("df_allyears_updated_variables_score.rds")
df <- tibble::as_tibble(df)
#nrow(df)  -- 386901

df <- filter(df, AGE >= 18)
#386811
df <- filter(df, PRG == 0)
# [1] 386749

# define the combined outcome
df$outcome <- ifelse(df$DIED == 0 & df$major_bleeding == 0 & df$acute_cerebral_ischemia == 0, "No", ifelse(df$DIED == 1 & df$major_bleeding == 0 & df$acute_cerebral_ischemia == 0, "death_only", ifelse(df$DIED == 0 & df$major_bleeding == 1 & df$acute_cerebral_ischemia == 0, "bleeding_only", ifelse(df$DIED == 0 & df$major_bleeding == 0 & df$acute_cerebral_ischemia == 1, "stroke_only", ifelse(df$DIED == 1 & df$major_bleeding == 1 & df$acute_cerebral_ischemia == 0, "death_bleeding", ifelse(df$DIED == 1 & df$major_bleeding == 0 & df$acute_cerebral_ischemia == 1, "death_stroke", ifelse(df$DIED == 0 & df$major_bleeding == 1 & df$acute_cerebral_ischemia == 1, "bleeding_stroke", ifelse(df$DIED == 1 & df$major_bleeding == 1 & df$acute_cerebral_ischemia == 1, "three_outcomes", "unknown"))))))))
df$outcome <- as.factor(df$outcome)

#delete individual outcomes
 df <- select(df, -c("event_acute_hemorrhagic_cva", "event_ocular_hemorrhage", "event_hemopericardium", "event_hemothorax", "event_hemoperitoneum", "event_hemoarthrosis", "event_cabg_bleeding", "event_bleeding_respiratory", "event_vaginal_bleeding", "event_hematuria", "event_hemorrhage_nonspecified", "event_pci_bleeding", "event_gi_bleeding", "blood_transfusion", "event_hemorrhagic_shock", "vasopressor_use", "event_posthemor_anemia", "other_measures", "bleeding_unknown", "bleeding_measures_1", "bleeding_measures_2", "bleeding_severe", "bleeding_measures", "NACE", "index", "ph"))

#delete Pregnancy variable
df <- select(df, -c("PRG"))

#################################################################################
################## Codes for 95% CI calculation #################################
#################################################################################
#install.packages("multiROC")
library(multiROC)
library(readr)
options(multicore = TRUE)

#load the csv file related to the model for what you want to calculate 95% CI
test_data <- read.csv("clf_rf_auc_refined.csv")
test_data <- test_data[,-1]

res <- multi_roc(test_data, force_diag=T)

unlist(res$AUC)

multi_roc_auc <- function(true_pred_data, idx) {
  results <- multi_roc(true_pred_data[idx, ])$AUC
  results <- unlist(results)
  return(results)
}

res_boot <- boot::boot(data=test_data, statistic=multi_roc_auc, R=1000)
saveRDS(res_boot, "res_boot_clf_rf.rds")
res_boot_ci <- boot::boot.ci(res_boot, type='norm', index=9)
res_boot_ci
